- St Louis Cardinals

+DOC ---
+SEQ

=VAL :Ken Griffey
-SEQ
-DOC

+SEQ
=VAL :Chicago Cubs
=VAL :St Louis Cardinals
-SEQ
-DOC
-STR

  "Sammy Sosa",
  "Ken Griffey"
]
[
  "Chicago Cubs",
  "St Louis Cardinals"
]

- Ken Griffey

+DOC ---
+MAP
=VAL :Time

=VAL :User
=VAL :ed
=VAL :Warning

-MAP
-DOC
+DOC ---
+MAP
=VAL :Time
=VAL :2001-11-23 15:02:31 -5
=VAL :User
=VAL :ed
=VAL :Warning
=VAL :A slightly different error message.
-MAP
-DOC
+DOC ---
+MAP
=VAL :Date
=VAL :2001-11-23 15:03:17 -5
=VAL :User
=VAL :ed

+MAP

=VAL :23

=VAL :58
